Package org.openbel.framework.core.compiler

Core compiler services (i.e., phases).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SemanticService Performs BEL semantic verification.
ValidationService  
 

Class Summary
DefaultValidationService Service to handle validation of statements.
SemanticServiceImpl BEL semantic service implementation.
ValidationResult Container Object to hold all warnings and errors that occurred as the result of a validation action.
 

Exception Summary
CreateKAMFailure A BEL KAM-creation failure, generated when saving a ProtoNetwork as a KAM.
ResourceSyntaxWarning A BEL Warning indicating there is a syntactical problem with a given value defined for a given resource location.
SemanticFailure A BEL warning indicating semantic verification has failed for a BEL document.
SemanticWarning A BEL warning indicating invalid BEL semantics were encountered.
SymbolWarning A BEL warning indicating an invalid symbol was encountered
ValidationError A BEL error indicating an error occurred validating XBEL XML content.
